|---|---|---|
| [context-registry.ts](file:///c:/Users/jonathan-moletta/.gemini/antigravity/playground/tensor-aurora/web/src/lib/context-registry.ts) | **4 objetos** `CONTEXT_MANIFESTS` definem estaticamente quais features existem em cada contexto | **Crítico** — adicionar/remover módulo requer deploy |
